  "A 200 g copper block (c = 385 J/(kg*C)) at 300 C is dropped into 500 g of water (c = 4186 J/(kg*C)) at 20 C. What is the equilibrium temperature?": "",
  "About 100 C": "",
  "About 160 C": "",
  "About 30 C": "",
  "About 55 C": "",
  "0.2(385)(300-T) = 0.5(4186)(T-20). 77(300-T) = 2093(T-20). 23100 - 77T = 2093T - 41860. 64960 = 2170T. T = 29.9 C.": "",
  "How much heat is needed to convert 2 kg of ice at -20 C to steam at 100 C? (c_ice = 2090 J/(kg*C), L_f = 334000 J/kg, c_water = 4186 J/(kg*C), L_v = 2.26 x 10^6 J/kg)": "",
  "About 6.1 MJ": "",
  "About 3.0 MJ": "",
  "About 9.0 MJ": "",
  "About 1.5 MJ": "",
  "Q = mc_ice(20) + mL_f + mc_water(100) + mL_v = 2[2090(20) + 334000 + 4186(100) + 2260000] = 2[41800+334000+418600+2260000] = 2(3054400) = 6.1 MJ.": "",
